5
00:00:18.833 --> 00:00:20.125
[in English] The studio.

6
00:00:20.208 --> 00:00:23.750
I... I like to mentally prepare for the day.

7
00:00:28.791 --> 00:00:29.791
I have to go.

8
00:00:30.541 --> 00:00:31.708
[Don] Ah. Zinhle.

9
00:00:31.791 --> 00:00:34.333
- [in Xhosa] If you think you can run away...
- [boy screams]

10
00:00:35.041 --> 00:00:37.541
- We'll find you.
- [screaming]

11
00:00:38.416 --> 00:00:39.500
[screaming]

12
00:00:40.333 --> 00:00:41.625
[screams fade]

13
00:00:45.125 --> 00:00:48.291
[in English] I saw your Durban photos.
Keep up the good work.

14
00:00:48.916 --> 00:00:49.916
Okay.

15
00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:57.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

16
00:01:01.875 --> 00:01:03.291
[glass cracking]

17
00:01:10.458 --> 00:01:11.708
