18
00:01:11.791 --> 00:01:13.250
- Mm-mm.
- So...

19
00:01:13.333 --> 00:01:16.458
[in Sotho] I'm sure they produce
thousands of bottles of bleach per month.

20
00:01:16.541 --> 00:01:18.958
Tell me. how are we going to do this?

21
00:01:19.750 --> 00:01:21.791
