25
00:01:30.208 --> 00:01:32.583
I will find a way to get in
and have a look around.

26
00:01:32.666 --> 00:01:33.708
Yeah. um...

27
00:01:33.791 --> 00:01:37.541
As long as some product survives for
the cosmetics bureau to investigate.

28
00:01:37.625 --> 00:01:39.625
[in English]
And I will take care of my side.

29
00:01:40.750 --> 00:01:43.541
[in Sotho] Uh. Zee. tell me something.

30
00:01:43.625 --> 00:01:46.833
Are you okay? You seem a bit distracted.

31
00:01:46.916 --> 00:01:48.375
No. I'm okay.

32
00:01:48.458 --> 00:01:50.125
And Ndu?

33
00:01:50.208 --> 00:01:51.333
It's over.

34
00:01:51.416 --> 00:01:53.136
[in English]
My head is back in the mission.

35
00:01:53.208 --> 00:01:55.500
[in Sotho] Good.
That's what I want to hear.

36
00:01:56.791 --> 00:01:57.791
Cheers.

37
00:02:03.958 --> 00:02:05.458
[engine starts]

38
00:02:13.541 --> 00:02:17.750
[Phila in English] It's a solid deal.
If he feels that nervous. then I can...

39
00:02:17.833 --> 00:02:19.291
I can see him this afternoon.

40
00:02:19.791 --> 00:02:21.708
Yeah. I can leave in a few minutes. and...

41
00:02:22.791 --> 00:02:23.791
Yeah.

42
00:02:25.250 --> 00:02:26.250
Yeah.

43
00:02:27.125 --> 00:02:30.666
Yeah. No. listen. just tell him
to calm down. okay. I'm going to...

44
00:02:31.208 --> 00:02:33.416
Yeah. I'm going to be there in 15 minutes.

45
00:02:33.500 --> 00:02:35.125
Ten minutes. okay. I...

46
00:02:35.208 --> 00:02:36.750
[sobbing softly]

47
00:02:36.833 --> 00:02:39.833
Hold on. I'm going to
have to call you back. Yeah? Cool.

48
00:02:41.166 --> 00:02:42.375
[sniffling]

49
00:02:45.458 --> 00:02:49.416
[clears throat] Zinhle. are you... Hey.

50
00:02:50.333 --> 00:02:53.083
- Oh. hey. What's going on?
- [Zinhle sighs]

51
00:02:53.166 --> 00:02:56.541
God. Sorry. This is so embarrassing.

52
00:02:56.625 --> 00:02:57.625
[sniffs]

53
00:02:57.708 --> 00:02:59.416
Ndu and I broke up.

54
00:03:01.500 --> 00:03:02.833
Right. Um...

55
00:03:02.916 --> 00:03:07.083
Yeah. he did mention
that things didn't go so well in Durban.

56
00:03:07.166 --> 00:03:09.000
Yeah. things were moving too fast.

57
00:03:09.791 --> 00:03:10.791
[sighs]

58
00:03:10.833 --> 00:03:12.375
I don't even know why I'm crying

59
00:03:12.458 --> 00:03:14.218
