who broke it off. [sniffles]

60
00:03:14.958 --> 00:03:16.666
Yeah. Well...

61
00:03:16.750 --> 00:03:21.625
So. what can I do? Is there
anything? Should I talk to him. maybe?

62
00:03:21.708 --> 00:03:22.708
No.

63
00:03:23.208 --> 00:03:24.625
No. thanks.

64
00:03:24.708 --> 00:03:28.291
I just... I just need to get
my mind off things. you know.

65
00:03:28.375 --> 00:03:29.500
go out or something.

66
00:03:29.583 --> 00:03:32.708
Right. That always works for me. So...

67
00:03:32.791 --> 00:03:34.916
- There's...
- Actually. now that I think about it.

68
00:03:35.000 --> 00:03:39.000
a friend of mine tried
to invite me to a party. and I...

69
00:03:39.083 --> 00:03:41.250
