70
00:03:41.333 --> 00:03:45.000
Actually. um. I got invited to this
warehouse party that sounds nice.

71
00:03:45.083 --> 00:03:46.416
You should come with me.

72
00:03:46.500 --> 00:03:48.833
Uh. no can do. I am done with partying.

73
00:03:48.916 --> 00:03:51.625
[in Zulu] Come on. it'll be fun.

74
00:03:51.708 --> 00:03:53.250
[in English] You love a good party.

75
00:03:53.333 --> 00:03:55.791
I can't really imagine
a better person to go with.

76
00:03:56.291 --> 00:03:58.083
Uh... Ah...

77
00:03:58.166 --> 00:03:59.208
Please.

78
00:04:05.666 --> 00:04:09.208
Okay. Okay. fine. fine. let's do it. Yeah?

79
00:04:09.291 --> 00:04:10.625
- Yeah.
- Okay.

80
00:04:11.208 --> 00:04:13.916
Um... Yeah. and chin up. by the way.

81
00:04:14.000 --> 00:04:16.625
You guys. I'm sure
you'll work things out. yeah.

82
00:04:17.333 --> 00:04:18.333
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

83
00:04:18.416 --> 00:04:19.625
- Okay.
- Thank you.

84
00:04:19.708 --> 00:04:20.708
Cool.

85
00:04:29.750 --> 00:04:33.958
[Kolobe in Zulu]
Sifiso. please go buy four fat cakes.

86
00:04:34.041 --> 00:04:35.041
Sharp.

87
00:04:40.791 --> 00:04:43.291
Please have a look at this.

88
00:04:52.666 --> 00:04:53.875
[chuckles]

89
00:05:03.250 --> 00:05:04.500
[Ndu in English] Yo. Zinhle.

90
00:05:05.375 --> 00:05:06.416
You going out?

91
00:05:07.583 --> 00:05:10.000
Listen. man. I was hoping we could talk.

92
00:05:10.083 --> 00:05:13.375
