when she's good and ready.

104
00:05:41.625 --> 00:05:43.041
I'll take care of her tonight.

105
00:05:45.000 --> 00:05:48.375
I mean I'm going to make sure
that no other guy tries to get in there.

106
00:05:49.625 --> 00:05:51.541
You know what? You're a good guy. okay.

107
00:05:51.625 --> 00:05:53.541
You are a good guy. and she knows it.

108
00:05:53.625 --> 00:05:56.250
Phila... Phila. watch it.

109
00:05:56.333 --> 00:05:59.166
["Dey My Side" by Worlasi playing]

110
00:05:59.250 --> 00:06:00.333
[engine starts]

111
00:06:12.833 --> 00:06:13.833
