112
00:06:16.208 --> 00:06:17.500
Ah. [clears throat]

113
00:06:18.416 --> 00:06:19.625
[in Sotho] Uh. hi.

114
00:06:19.708 --> 00:06:20.875
Hi.

115
00:06:23.666 --> 00:06:25.041
Are you looking for something?

116
00:06:26.000 --> 00:06:28.250
Um... No.

117
00:06:29.583 --> 00:06:32.083
I'm just waiting for Mbali.

118
00:06:33.250 --> 00:06:34.250
Mbali?

119
00:06:34.333 --> 00:06:37.375
Yes. she works at New Point.

120
00:06:37.458 --> 00:06:39.125
Do you know her?

121
00:06:39.208 --> 00:06:41.000
I don't know her.

122
00:06:42.333 --> 00:06:43.791
Tell me something.

123
00:06:44.625 --> 00:06:46.166
have we met before?

124
00:06:47.541 --> 00:06:48.750
No.

125
00:06:49.875 --> 00:06:51.375
- Are you sure?
- Yes. I'm sure.

126
00:06:53.708 --> 00:06:54.708
Okay.

127
00:06:57.541 --> 00:06:59.625
You can't park here.

128
00:06:59.708 --> 00:07:00.958
[engine starts]

129
00:07:01.041 --> 00:07:02.041
Sure.

130
00:07:02.833 --> 00:07:03.833
Cheers. sir.

131
00:07:12.458 --> 00:07:14.976
[Zinhle in English] You do know
McDonald's is not dinner. right?

132
00:07:15.000 --> 00:07:16.541
