140
00:07:36.208 --> 00:07:37.791
I don't mind.

141
00:07:37.875 --> 00:07:39.750
You and Ndu. what happened?

142
00:07:39.833 --> 00:07:43.666
Because. I mean. he hasn't
been serious about anyone in. like. years.

143
00:07:44.500 --> 00:07:45.708
Um...

144
00:07:45.791 --> 00:07:48.250
I'd rather not talk about that right now.

145
00:07:50.500 --> 00:07:52.125
Okay. fair enough.

146
00:07:53.250 --> 00:07:55.750
[automated voice]
<i>At the next intersection. turn left.</i>

147
00:07:57.458 --> 00:08:00.958
Um. where did you say
that this place that we're going to is?

148
00:08:02.041 --> 00:08:04.000
Let me... let me just check.

149
00:08:06.083 --> 00:08:07.125
[Phila] Okay.

150
00:08:07.833 --> 00:08:09.833
[chain clattering]

151
00:08:10.958 --> 00:08:14.291
["Friends" playing]

152
00:08:14.375 --> 00:08:16.375
<i>♪ You know how to run ♪</i>

153
00:08:21.333 --> 00:08:23.291
<i>♪ You know how to hide ♪</i>

154
00:08:26.375 --> 00:08:28.166
