158
00:08:35.875 --> 00:08:37.416
<i>♪ You know your price ♪</i>

159
00:08:41.833 --> 00:08:43.833
<i>♪ Your little friends ♪</i>

160
00:08:48.541 --> 00:08:51.083
<i>♪ Do you wanna think twice? ♪</i>

161
00:08:55.458 --> 00:08:58.291
<i>♪ Have you ever been this far? ♪</i>

162
00:09:01.958 --> 00:09:03.125
[door clanks]

163
00:09:44.791 --> 00:09:47.041
[song continues]

164
00:10:02.375 --> 00:10:03.625
[liquid sloshes]

165
00:10:05.541 --> 00:10:10.333
It's a warehouse by day
and a secret party spot by night.

166
00:10:10.416 --> 00:10:12.125
Why do you ask? Is there a problem?

167
00:10:12.208 --> 00:10:16.541
No. no. I just kind of
recognize the... the neighborhood.

168
00:10:16.625 --> 00:10:19.083
You know. the last time
I was at a warehouse party

169
00:10:19.166 --> 00:10:21.750
was. like. four or five years ago. So...

170
00:10:22.250 --> 00:10:23.125
Yeah.

171
00:10:23.208 --> 00:10:24.083
[both laugh]

172
00:10:24.166 --> 00:10:26.726
- I've actually never been to one.
- [automated voice]<i>...turn right.</i>

173
00:10:26.750 --> 00:10:28.833
