174
00:10:28.916 --> 00:10:30.000
Uh-huh.

175
00:10:30.083 --> 00:10:32.541
- [automated voice]<i> Turn right.</i>
- Right. Phila. Right.

176
00:10:32.625 --> 00:10:35.541
I know. I know. I heard you. okay.
I'm just making a quick stop.

177
00:10:35.625 --> 00:10:37.291
