178
00:10:37.375 --> 00:10:40.166
Yeah. well. you don't arrive early
to a party. anyway.

179
00:10:40.250 --> 00:10:42.208
So. relax. please.

180
00:10:42.291 --> 00:10:46.041
[automated voice] <i>You're driving in
the wrong direction. Please turn around.</i>

181
00:11:31.500 --> 00:11:33.083
- Hello?
- [operator] <i>This is 911.</i>

182
00:11:33.166 --> 00:11:36.916
Yes. there's a warehouse on fire
on 11th Street.

183
00:11:37.666 --> 00:11:40.375
Yes. on 11th Street. It's on fire!

184
00:11:40.458 --> 00:11:42.208
[operator speaking indistinctly]

185
00:11:43.041 --> 00:11:44.125
[phone clicks off]

186
00:11:48.541 --> 00:11:50.750
[Zinhle sighs] What are we waiting for?

187
00:11:50.833 --> 00:11:52.208
MDMA.

188
00:11:52.291 --> 00:11:53.333
What?

189
00:11:54.041 --> 00:11:56.041
You said you wanted to have a good time.

190
00:11:56.791 --> 00:11:59.458
Bab' Don would not
approve of us taking drugs.

191
00:11:59.541 --> 00:12:01.625
Well. I'm not gonna tell if you don't.

192
00:12:01.708 --> 00:12:02.750
Phila. please.

193
00:12:02.833 --> 00:12:05.833
I don't want to worry about you
all night because you're high on MMA.

194
00:12:05.916 --> 00:12:07.541
I said MDMA. M...

195
00:12:07.625 --> 00:12:09.541
Or whatever that is.

196
00:12:11.333 --> 00:12:15.000
All right. just wait here.
I'll be back in a second.

197
00:12:19.791 --> 00:12:21.166
Shit!

198
00:12:23.458 --> 00:12:24.708
Ugh!

199
00:12:24.791 --> 00:12:26.166
[cell phone chimes]

200
00:12:34.083 --> 00:12:37.250
All right. I told you
I would not take long.

201
00:12:39.041 --> 00:12:39.916
Ta-da!

202
00:12:40.000 --> 00:12:42.333
You're not going to take that now. right?

203
00:12:43.708 --> 00:12:44.916
No. I'm not.

204
00:12:47.833 --> 00:12:50.291
- All right. ready?
- Yes!

205
00:12:50.375 --> 00:12:51.833
Let's do this.

206
00:12:54.458 --> 00:12:56.458
[fire crackling]

207
00:12:59.708 --> 00:13:00.916
Shit.

208
00:13:15.958 --> 00:13:16.833
Shit.

209
00:13:16.916 --> 00:13:20.083
[in Sotho] Zinhle. there will be
nothing left if you don't get here soon.

210
00:13:21.416 --> 00:13:23.666
