211
00:13:24.916 --> 00:13:26.208
Somebody help!

212
00:13:27.000 --> 00:13:28.000
[sighs]

213
00:13:29.958 --> 00:13:31.166
[glass cracking]

214
00:13:34.375 --> 00:13:36.833
[Kolobe] Is somebody there? Help!

215
00:13:36.916 --> 00:13:38.916
[coughing]

216
00:13:56.625 --> 00:13:58.625
[smoke alarm beeping]

217
00:14:00.750 --> 00:14:02.125
[coughing]

218
00:14:02.666 --> 00:14:03.666
