219
00:14:06.458 --> 00:14:08.416
- [Kolobe in Sotho] It's you.
- [Bonga] Huh?

220
00:14:08.916 --> 00:14:10.000
[Kolobe] It's you.

221
00:14:11.041 --> 00:14:12.250
